Igntius laughed to himself. The chip was doing the talking for this 
bot. She couldn't help it. The minute it's taken off the minute she 
realizes what a monster he is. But he can't tell her that. He just 
continued flying.

"That's great. If you want to make him happy, go right ahead."

The Trainers kept heading towards the Ark.

(Be back soon!)
